{"tid":1552283,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］警方決定將黃之鋒通宵扣查","createTime":"2019-09-08T10:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:21:33.000Z","uid":22556,"like":316,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"1af0f616ee4cd69728597e0a5752d39b0186bae0","tid":1552283,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:02:27.000Z","msg":"【聲明】<br />\n(Please scroll down for English)<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒透過律師作出以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n一、今早我在機場離境時被警方以「違反保釋條件」為由拘捕，現時被扣留。<br />\n<br />\n二、初步法律意見指出，法庭於8月30日批出保釋時已知悉並准許我前往德國及美國，故相信是保釋內容手誤。預計明早九時三十分聆訊澄清後可獲釋。希望各位朋友不用擔心。<br />\n<br />\n三、相信今次事件並非刻意針對本人，但我認為警方濫捕濫告的後果，造成今次雙輸的局面。同時，今次顯然只屬行政程序問題，但警方仍然決意將我通宵扣留，我認為極度不合理。<br />\n<br />\n2019年9月8日<br />\n<br />\nSTATEMENT<br />\n08 SEPTEMBER 2019<br />\n<br />\nJoshua Wong delivered the following message through his legal representative: <br />\n<br />\nI was arrested by police for &ldquo;breaching bail conditions&rdquo; this morning at the Airport&rsquo;s customs and I am detained in custody now. <br />\n<br />\nPreliminary legal advice suggested that the Court had acknowledged and approved my trips to Germany and the US when it granted bail on August 30. Therefore, it is believed that there are some mistakes have been made on the bail certificate. It is expected that I will be released after the hearing tomorrow morning so I hope fellow friends not to worry too much. <br />\n<br />\nI believe the ridiculous circumstance I&rsquo;m facing now is the direct consequence of the political prosecution and arrest. It also reflects the maladministration of HK government as by making these mistakes, it leads to the lose-lose situation now we are facing, even though I believe today&rsquo;s incident is nothing personal against me. <br />\n<br />\nI&rsquo;m also discontented to police&rsquo;s decision to detain me overnight, despite a clear procedural hiccup, which is utterly unreasonable.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2462194093873084?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2462194093873084%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=191be7ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2462194093873084?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"f8cc830cbe94fd27cf9aa7d1fadb160dd8f87d72","tid":1552283,"uid":20723,"like":173,"dislike":2,"score":171,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK4c%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=6da79077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢"},{"pid":"ed896e8d976e6b5392ba91e214d09b5e080a2e1b","tid":1552283,"uid":82640,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"popo on9"},{"pid":"46b84fee592d4f102b6b4cfe934ca1f3934ef6ad","tid":1552283,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8cc830cbe94fd27cf9aa7d1fadb160dd8f87d72","tid":1552283,"uid":20723,"like":173,"dislike":2,"score":171,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://